{"tid":1477222,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"[急急急]  BNO 平權唔夠人簽，請入來簽","createTime":"2019-08-16T05:13:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-23T10:31:54.000Z","uid":57891,"like":36,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":61,"replies":[{"pid":"76ec2f655e4296233349dc82c12f2eaaa39d0b42","tid":1477222,"uid":57891,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T05:13:24.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://petition.parliament.uk/petitions/244402\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetition.parliament.uk%2Fpetitions%2F244402&d=bx%2Fd%2Fc%2BwyKmxZhRK7gjal1uXAffr%2FfAYLX%2F1af%2FGhNY%3D&h=03859f72\" target=\"_blank\">https://petition.parliament.uk/petitions/244402</a><br />\n<br />\n要十萬人支持。<br />\n<br />\n香港人 加油"},{"pid":"b022f4768b3877619dbe5c129e91e83148ec2657","tid":1477222,"uid":169048,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T05:20:43.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n平左權手足無後顧之憂"},{"pid":"f332a666e69dd6e995abe7d08d0af6e05c81ea36","tid":1477222,"uid":57891,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T05:22:15.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"12a62cab67561704aa5e33632477ed482fa9d55c","tid":1477222,"uid":57891,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T05:41:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2e3565e8d01d98ddbbe6ed7adf98af09b0f8acb0","tid":1477222,"uid":57891,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T05:41:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c52c21c72100610a4f5cfc5c50679d99db6537f","tid":1477222,"uid":305971,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T05:43:12.000Z","msg":"推，我00後冇BNO都幫吓手簽"},{"pid":